# create http tests for the address module using the rest client extension

### Autocomplete
GET http://localhost:3000/api/address/autocomplete?q=123 Main

###
GET http://localhost:3000/api/address/autocomplete?q=123 Main HTTP/1.1
### Place
GET http://localhost:3000/api/address/place/123 Main
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address": "123 Main St, Atlanta, GA 30303"
}
### Validate
POST http://localhost:3000/api/address/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address": "123 Main St, Atlanta, GA 30303"
}
### Reverse Geocode
POST http://localhost:3000/api/address/reverse-geocode
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "latitude": 33.749,
    "longitude": -84.388
}
### Service Check
POST http://localhost:3000/api/address/service-check
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "address": {
        "latitude": 33.749,
        "longitude": -84.388
    },
    "store": {
        "id": "s1",
        "latitude": 33.749,
        "longitude": -84.388,
        "radiusKm": 10
    }
}